Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:19.33,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:25.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:30.93,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:36.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:43.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:48.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:53.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:58.06,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:06.64,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Slicing through the darkness, they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:12.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}that blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:17.31,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:24.33,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.52,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,134)}BOOBY TRAP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.31,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\)\x98.75\y98.75}The year was AD 1999.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.10,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The object that had suddenly\Ncrashed into the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:52.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,was a gigantic space battleship\Nover 1,200 meters in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.07,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's technology was far in\Nadvance of mankind's own,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and while no trace of alien beings\Ncould be found aboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.16,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,it was clear that extraterrestrial civilizations\Ndid indeed exist beyond our planet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:07.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and that they had made the\Nstars their battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.63,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,This prompted both the founding of the\NEarth United Nations Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.79,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,which would take precedence over the\Ninterests of the individual nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and a concerted effort to restore\Nthe hulking spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:21.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But the road to establishing the Earth UN\NGovernment wasn't an easy one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:26.31,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and brush-fire wars\Nsprang up across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:32.33,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite this, restoration of the\Nbattleship progressed steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.56,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the long and painful\N"Unification Wars" came to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.98,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Earth was once again at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.70,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, this wrecked craft of alien design\Nwas rebuilt by humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and was reborn as the giant\Nbattleship "Macross."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.62,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,It is now ten years since the Macross\Ncrash-landed on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...\NToday may be the last day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:37.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll get to see the Macross.\NI'll miss its constant presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I wonder if that\Nmonstrosity will even fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wonder what will happen\Nto our local businesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's a VIP... \Nsomeone who invested a lot in the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably headed for the launch\Nceremony, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Captain Global?\NGot a hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens are out here to celebrate\Nthe launch of your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you showing some appreciation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NOh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!\N1st Lieutenant Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the captain has\Narrived at the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have fifteen minutes until\Nthe ceremony starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We might just make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the captain has\Nbeen doing this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably out partying,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He left last night saying something about\Nthe Earth Defense Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That sly old fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you would do anything like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Oh? Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Major Focker came home\Ntogether this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite the celebrity around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying out all night won't affect my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:56.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}You may be fine, but the major has to\Nfly escort for the Macross later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that man can drink all night\Nand not feel it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He always brags about shooting down five\Nfighters in the Unification Wars while hung over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, if something were to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine! I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps you'd like to take him off my hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have him! He's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:18.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Even OUR 1st Lieutenant\Nis interested in men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a terrible thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To think, 1st Lieutenant Hayase, the top\Ngraduate from the academy, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:25.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Look at the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:37.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Small craft approaching on heading 1057,\Nplease state your affiliation, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hikaru Ichijo, invitation\Nnumber 1021. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed.\NYou were invited by Major Focker, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please proceed along vector 1069, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:47.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.51,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now present an aerobatics\Ndemonstration performed by
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.22,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,our newest, most powerful fighter:\Nthe Valkyrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.20,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Commentary will be provided by the Ace of the\NUnification Wars...Major Roy Focker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep your eyes on planes 2 and 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:17.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They will pass each other at 950 km/h,\Nonly 20 meters above the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, the two planes will be\Njust a few meters apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!\NIt's you, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that voice...\NSempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"How have you been?!"\NWhat a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru! What the hell are you doing,\Nputtering around up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's pretty cold, considering you were\Nthe one who sent me the invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked you to come buzzing in\Nhere in a prop plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:02.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe my ass! Besides, you could never keep\Nup with me, so don't go talking all big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't always be in your shadow, Sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:07.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:15.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:47.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get so g...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what the hell was that\Nlittle stunt just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:00.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a boost to an inverted climb.\NYou taught me that yourself, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, those military pilots were\Npretty good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, kid, don't get cocky\Njust because you won
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Amateur Pilot Competition\Ntwo or three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the other\Nfour or so times?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven times?\NBig deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Unification Wars, I shot\Ndown more than 180 planes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"M...Murderer"?\NLook, it's not like I had a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:31.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you made a promise to\Nmy dad, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:34.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That you'd come back to the team\Nonce the war was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I let your dad down,\Nand I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you start flying fighters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you ever do,\Nyou'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have changed, Sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cola!\NI wanna have a cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}No!\NI'm not going to buy you any!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had some juice a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Cola! Cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make you want to use the restroom! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}You see?\NHere we go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pee my pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's one thing about you\Nthat sure hasn't changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:57.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their de-fold signature was tracked\Nhere, to this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any sign of a re-fold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we have detected no indications\Nof a second hyperspace jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:11.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But they should've been withdrawing\Nfrom this region eight {\i1}taarms{\i0} ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the signature is from some\Nother ship that was shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough information\Nto make a determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:16.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Send out a recon ship to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of those new fighters,\Nlike the ones from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, wanna take this baby up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the back seat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? This is one of those fighter\Nplanes you hate so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends on who's using it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:43.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You never shut up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross has ushered in vast\Nimprovements in individual welfare
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and has profoundly contributed to\Nthe development of humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Macross is launched, Earth's\Ndefenses will finally be complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:53.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Captain Global.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just received a message\Nfrom Space Carrier ARMD-I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They've detected anomalies in\Nthe gravitational field
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and luminescent phenomena\Noriginating in lunar orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravitational anomalies and\Nluminescent phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the Macross arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:15.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me introduce the commander\Nof the Macross, Captain Global!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Captain? Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,W...What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:21.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The ship's original systems have\Njust activated themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:25.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!\NIt's entered firing mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down all systems!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! They're not responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The main cannon is activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:25.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it was hiding on the planet after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all ships!\NAdvance into the strike zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The... The ship's systems are back\Nunder our control, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that was one flashy salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right...\NI'll go check things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, you stay right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Star-class code.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:21.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The beam from the main cannon has\Ndestroyed what appears to have been
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,a spaceship in lunar orbit,\Nat a range of 280,000 km.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:27.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple additional spacecraft detected\Nand they're closing in rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:43.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a booby trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"A booby trap"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,German troops often used them\Nduring the Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They would hide explosives in things\Nthat would get attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,like pens or guns, and then they'd retreat,\Nleaving those things behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When somebody picked the object up...\NBOOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet the aliens that crashed\Nthis ship planted a program
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,that controlled an\Nautomatic defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:07.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No smoking is allowed on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Shammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I know that!\NI was just keeping it in my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, Level One combat alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What... Just what were\Nthose weapons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:27.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But no, it couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Two enemy vessels approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe they are the craft that\Nlaunched the weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't seem to be part of\Nthe Supervision Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Plow through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Message from ARMD-II.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,ARMD-I is out of commission, and ARMD-II\Nhas sustained minor damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy fleet has broken through\Nthe space defense perimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and is headed straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Earth Defense Council yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,it was decided that if the Macross\Nlaunched into space today
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and were to eventually encounter\Nan alien race
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,under no circumstances were\Nwe to initiate hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch all fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!\NAll fighters, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:43.52,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently engaged in\Nhostilities with alien forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:44.97,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.08,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, this is not a drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Another war, huh?\NIt's been two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.52,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost Squadrons, launch complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Focker!\NLaunch the Valkyrie Squadrons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NThey're completely disorganized!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This must surely be a primitive species.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So they DID find the Supervision Army ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This type of vessel is not in my records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:37.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in your records?\NBut you're the Chief Archivist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, it seems to resemble\Nthe weapons of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean that they\Nfound this ship and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Restored it.\NYes, it's quite possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:50.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that such a primitive species\Ncould possibly possess the lost technology!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:55.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits the facts.\NIt would also explain the missiles we saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The long-lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaction weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's the case, we cannot\Njustify destroying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,J'nerl target pinpointed.\NNow launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,VT-102!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:37.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,VT-102 on the display grounds!\NWhy haven't you taken off yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,VT-102?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:39.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around!\NTake off at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off?!\NBut the runway's a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:06.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:48.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Skull Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all fighters in\NSepia and Mountain Teams:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,scatter and take down the\Nenemy in zone 428!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Focker-Sempai!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:04.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you become a fighter pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:11.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking!\NLike I'd ever become a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?!\NHikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Hikaru. What happened to that\Nhotshot attitude you had earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:30.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hikaru. Flying in formation like this\Nfeels just like the old days, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so laid-back\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always in front, and you'd be\Nputtering around behind me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I?\NI'm not gonna be in your shadow forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit.\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:54.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:58.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:16.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:21.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore that when I died, it'd be during\Na stunt, just like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:25.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,VT-102!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:28.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a collision course with us!\NVeer off at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:29.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:30.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudders and spoilers are fried,\Nand nothing else is responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just change to Configuration B?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:38.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Configuration B?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what that is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:41.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:46.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, pull the "B" lever on the left of\Nyour console and engage ACS!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:47.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:51.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:41.85,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Still not clear what's happening around him,\NIchijo finds himself drawn into the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:46.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst the flames of battle awaits a\Nfateful encounter: Lynn Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:50.83,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru has no way of knowing\Njust how important...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:53.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,...this beautiful young girl will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.69,0:23:57.40,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"COUNT DOWN"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:23.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.34,0:24:29.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}the shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.04,0:24:36.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}We all keep running until the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:44.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}but we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:50.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.19,0:24:56.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.13,0:25:04.38,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:16.08,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,38)}the light that shines so far away
